_sText: ************************************************************* README FIRST: I was bored and had no real new ideas for my current wip: surf japan remake. So i played all my surfmaps and the fizzycave was funny but short and had no lightning. So i edited it for our server and now its real different from the original i think... ************************************************************* MAP INFOS: - 48 spawns - lightning - extended the map - complete new jail - new weapons - extras on long path - secret buyzone - ambient sounds ************************************************************* CREDITS: Blobby Mahn did the original one so thanks to him ( i hope to see more from u ^^ ) *************************************************************
